4. We intially tried:
  cat dump.txt | grep picoCTF
5. However, it did not return anything useful. We then manually inspected the ASCII output in dump.txt. We use gedit to inspect dump.txt and use "ctrl + f" to search for keywords.
  gedit dump.txt
6. We discovered the flag embedded within the image data.
